  "content": "=\"tag\">CUDA</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 24px; font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-muted);\">\n      github.com/chunzhe10/corvia\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">01 / 08</div>\n</div>\n<!-- SLIDE 2: THE PROBLEM — visual bottleneck diagram -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Problem</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    Two Workloads.<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-red\">One GPU.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 36px;\">\n    <span class=\"corvia-wm\">corvia</span>'s inference server runs embeddings (vector search) and LLM chat (reasoning).<br>\n    Both are GPU-hungry. Both were fighting over the same card.\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Before: both crammed into RTX -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <!-- Embedding workload -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 2px solid var(--accent-cyan); border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">&#128270;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cyan);\">Embeddings</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">ONNX Runtime</div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Plus sign -->\n    <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-red);\">+</div>\n    <!-- Chat workload -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); border: 2px solid var(--accent-purple); border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">&#129504;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-purple);\">LLM Chat</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">llama.cpp</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Arrow down to bottleneck -->\n  <div class=\"arrow-down\">&#11015;</div>",
